---
import SectionContainer from "../SectionContainer.astro";
const colores = [
    "bg-[#BCC2AB]",
    "bg-[#D9A3A2]",
    "bg-[#E1DADB]",
    "bg-[#E2B7A8]",
    "bg-[#F3E0D8]",
]
---
<SectionContainer bgColor="pt-24">
    <section class="text-white rounded-2xl relative h-[646px]"> 
        <div class={`w-full absolute -top-4 h-1/2 ${colores[0]} -z-10 rounded-2xl`}> 
        </div>
        <div class={`w-full absolute -top-8 h-1/2 ${colores[1]} -z-20 rounded-2xl`}> 
        </div>
        <div class={`w-full absolute -top-12 h-1/2 ${colores[2]} -z-30 rounded-2xl`}> 
        </div>
        <div class={`w-full absolute -top-16 h-1/2 ${colores[3]} -z-40 rounded-2xl`}> 
        </div>
        <div class={`w-full absolute -top-20 h-1/2 ${colores[4]} -z-50 rounded-2xl`}> 
        </div>
        <img class="object-cover object-center h-full rounded-2xl" src="/img/img-2-dresscode.jpg " alt="">
        <div class="z-20 absolute w-full top-10 text-center ">
            <h2 class="font-sf-bold text-3xl">Dresscode</h2>
            <p>
                Código de vestimenta e ideas para vestir
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="z-20 absolute w-full bottom-10 space-y-5 text-center px-5">
            <section>
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-1">
                    {
                        colores.map((color) => (
                            <span class={`flex w-7 h-7 me-3 ${color} rounded-full `}></span>
                        ))
                    }
                </div>
                <p class="font-sf-semibold">Colores sugeridos</p>
            </section>
            <p class="">Te sugerimos estos colores para vestidos, y abajo te dejamos una colección en Pinterest para que puedas tener un panorama mas amplio de colores y formas de vestidos</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-sf-semibold">La única regla es <span class="text-[#B3FF12]">no</span> vestir color blanco y color rojo</p>
            <section class="z-20 flex justify-center items-center gap-3">
                <a href="" class=" text-sm  rounded-full transition-all duration-150 hover:opacity-80 primary-button  px-16 py-3 font-sf-light">Ir a pinterest</a>
            </section>
        </div>
        <section class="w-full bottom-0 absolute bg-gradient-to-t from-stone-950 to-transparent h-1/2 rounded-b-xl"></section>
    </section>
</SectionContainer>